382c14a08af800cb38758","tid":490614,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"chem真係勸你慎重考慮<br />\n我yr1 都打算揀chem major 不過workload大 lab 又多（cu）最後放棄左<br />\n而且每日對住d化學物身體都會差埋"},{"pid":"b80e6a6afc1a35d860b32ca0be43cbc4c69d01c0","tid":490614,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Chem呢d咁多間大學都有既科<br />\n一定係睇大學知名度架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三大 &gt; 其他<br />\n<br />\nScience係香港既出路係冇出路</blockquote><br />\n但如果做化驗難唔難搵工</blockquote><br />\n依加化驗易搵到爆<br />\n到到公證行都缺人<br />\n有手有腳都請<br />\n不過人工就唔好咁高期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8362fc4c4510d6a093313532534e679fac2f255","tid":490614,"uid":49481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:16:11.000Z","msg":"唔好呀樓主讀engine,nursing都好過sci呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 回頭是岸呀"},{"pid":"afcfb8d9ebf87ce2f9c1413492bc530a2fd63f8e","tid":490614,"uid":95577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>chem真係勸你慎重考慮<br />\n我yr1 都打算揀chem major 不過workload大 lab 又多（cu）最後放棄左<br />\n而且每日對住d化學物身體都會差埋</blockquote><br />\nCU chem喺Science入邊唔算最慘果堆<br />\nLab report又有source, assignment 又係<br />\n考試又翻炒試題<br />\nMaths同Phy先係最慘，workload又重，啲野又難，仲要係乞食科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e156986ff2e21c6a3183875d4fed81c3777d5c4","tid":490614,"uid":157107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\nCu science major biochem係咪真係會chur死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽人講biochem出路最好"},{"pid":"75cd2da62685fe2f527e4c77b553ddd7679aa78a","tid":490614,"uid":53941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問<br />\nCu science major biochem係咪真係會chur死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽人講biochem出路最好</blockquote><br />\nBiochem 好多神人<br />\n本身churchur地<br />\n但同神人競爭會chur到hihi<br />\n除非想third hon grad"},{"pid":"cac96ffbf3cc7e953c394aaa25a256a89c3c3a15","tid":490614,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答你<br />\n<br />\nbu sci講名氣輸哂，所以有得揀當然去其他u<br />\n<br />\n冇學習氣氛就睇你識咩人架啫，有摺友日日溫書，<br />\n有人堂都唔上又唔溫書，所以都係睇你自己個人<br />\n<br />\n講出路，間間u sci都唔太好，不過bu仔點同其他u比<br />\n<br />\n不過如果唔想太chur， sci又唔算太勁嘅，咪入bu囉。因為成班人都唔勁，讀落幾開心嘅...<br />\n<br />\n利申：原本諗住reject offer, 不過冇勇氣，但係讀緊又唔覺咩大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為想做化驗相關既工作 見到佢果科個title 諗緊會唔會呢科畢業後會比起純讀chem既三大有優勢<br />\n定其實搵化驗相關既工 人地都係睇u多過睇major<br />\n<br />\nBtw多謝你仔細回覆 我可以考慮得更充足<br />\n因為唔係驚chur 只係初時諗果科個title好似直接同化驗相關"},{"pid":"d3b2e67d649cd4caa1880190c05c9f3419524a6d","tid":490614,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:11:22.000Z","msg":"三大sci都食緊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71fc6864946f033ebbe4022300fd20a77ae1549","tid":490614,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你醒啦<br />\nscience吃屎㗎<br />\n仲要係chem<br />\n死路一條</blockquote><br />\n睇黎大家意見一致地覺得sci冇出路<br />\n等我再諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ba9b22dc2faea927ebd315e467f29de70ffd9f","tid":490614,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>chem真係勸你慎重考慮<br />\n我yr1 都打算揀chem major 不過workload大 lab 又多（cu）最後放棄左<br />\n而且每日對住d化學物身體都會差埋</blockquote><br />\n明白 即係本身你係對chem有興趣？<br />\n咁有冇諗住畢業後做咩野工"},{"pid":"0844fbc939a3a45f88bbc3415e49877fc9a70a14","tid":490614,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"讀Science 等乞食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b08ee5d1d858aa9b1cfd8976949bf8539855b7c","tid":490614,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Chem呢d咁多間大學都有既科<br />\n一定係睇大學知名度架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三大 &gt; 其他<br />\n<br />\nScience係香港既出路係冇出路</blockquote><br />\n但如果做化驗難唔難搵工</blockquote><br />\n依加化驗易搵到爆<br />\n到到公證行都缺人<br />\n有手有腳都請<br />\n不過人工就唔好咁高期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係其實唔駛一定讀化驗都入到去做？"},{"pid":"af41bfc4eedc2b304600bd88d45d7fce830630e7","tid":490614,"uid":19062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"Bu science 只揀cs<br />\n唔係出到黎真係唔好諗錢途"},{"pid":"0ab51aa59cba16a48b0a36f4450f8373a55e2de5","tid":490614,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67558f6dcead7a6afa8ea13d3870f78c6d277bab","tid":490614,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n但如果做化驗難唔難搵工</blockquote><br />\n依加化驗易搵到爆<br />\n到到公證行都缺人<br />\n有手有腳都請<br />\n不過人工就唔好咁高期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係其實唔駛一定讀化驗都入到去做？</blockquote><br />\n基本上要求讀化學、化驗果類<br />\n都聽過有唔相關科入到去做，不過極少數<br />\n同埋你乜野理論都唔識入去鳩做，同工廠係無分別，而且應該唔會俾學run機"},{"pid":"8dcbe4445d550cf1c6148d8a152b421c69044804","tid":490614,"uid":50554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>BU science-&gt;藥廠<br />\nGrad左1年月入ard 30-35k</blockquote><br />\n認真post就咪害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔信咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藥廠sales老底18K+佣<br />\n當然大部分人都唔係做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人去PDGE有人做補習"},{"pid":"f5bdc57479018f2392f8d9d63c4ca0a77413a0cf","tid":490614,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"504c5e8f7a4aaec17e780e7389a202addfa57b55","tid":490614,"uid":155346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真答你<br />\n<br />\nbu sci講名氣輸哂，所以有得揀當然去其他u<br />\n<br />\n冇學習氣氛就睇你識咩人架啫，有摺友日日溫書，<br />\n有人堂都唔上又唔溫書，所以都係睇你自己個人<br />\n<br />\n講出路，間間u sci都唔太好，不過bu仔點同其他u比<br />\n<br />\n不過如果唔想太chur， sci又唔算太勁嘅，咪入bu囉。因為成班人都唔勁，讀落幾開心嘅...<br />\n<br />\n利申：原本諗住reject offer, 不過冇勇氣，但係讀緊又唔覺咩大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為想做化驗相關既工作 見到佢果科個title 諗緊會唔會呢科畢業後會比起純讀chem既三大有優勢<br />\n定其實搵化驗相關既工 人地都係睇u多過睇major<br />\n<br />\nBtw多謝你仔細回覆 我可以考慮得更充足<br />\n因為唔係驚chur 只係初時諗果科個title好似直接同化驗相關</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三大好D 讀testing 唔會比到優勢你 因為testing 唔會真係學多好多，你入三大major analytical chem 仲會殺食 <br />\n<br />\n利申讀緊Polyu testing 發現chem major 都同我搶緊工，其他人仲可以去做藥廠sales 不過我就只可以做化驗<br />\n如果真係鍾意做化驗"},{"pid":"f5b7c54d0f684a7e7abd4a40649b1c7a5f2404ca","tid":490614,"uid":44878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解咁多人話bu science垃圾<br />\nCity 科 chem呢咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多科嘅風評係冇得解，就算同U嘅人都唔會完全明白其他科系究竟發生咩事。<br />\n<br />\n依啲野入到U，坐到落課室上堂自然會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n但去到個時如果後悔，就已經係諗Quit唔Quit U嘅時候啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝你睇完依度咁多過來人嘅分享，揀啱科啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73948ced1c02e053fea2d19abf125a65000c86c","tid":490614,"uid":142754